docs.text: Welcome to deeplexicon Docs deeplexicon is a tool to demultiplex barcodeded nanopore direct RNA sequencing data, as well as train the models to do so. Code: deeplexicon . Pre-print: Barcoding and demultiplexing Oxford Nanopore native RNA sequencing reads with deep residual learning ....Large update in progress.... Overview Getting help with SquiggleKit Happy to help and receive feedback. You can leave an issue on the github repo: deeplexicon , @Psy_Fer_ on twitter, or shoot me an email at j.ferguson@garvan.org.au Created and maintained by James Ferguson from Genomic Technologies, Kinghorn Centre for Clinical Genomics, Garvan Institute , Sydney Australia.
